--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.1 (2018-11-30)
I: Define default value for 'item.state' parameter

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-10-20)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.3.2 (2018-05-17)
B: Correct template path

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-04-24)
I: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-04-04)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.3
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.2

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-02-20)
I: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 0.1.0 (2017-09-04)
F: Initial release
